highlighted_text:
if they are mindful of God,

believe, and do good deeds;

then are still mindful of God

and believe;

then are still mindful of God

and do better deeds—

for God loves those who do good.

If God touches you

with affliction, none but He

can remove it;

if Satan makes you forget,

then, when you remember,

sit apart from those who do wrong.

You who believe, seek help

through patience and prayer;

God is with those who show patience.

For all in the heavens and on earth

submit to Him, willing or unwilling;

they shall be brought back to Him.
